>MongoDb is NoSql DB
>Mongoose is a package-manager for mongoDb

>mkdir mongo-demo
>cd mongo-demo
>npm init -y		#To initialze the package.json
>npm -i mongoose	#Gives us simple APIs to work with mongoDB.
>code .
>create index.js	#In VSCode


Mongoose Methods:
-----------------
>mongoose.connect('URL/IP')	#To connnet to the DB
>mongoose.schema		#To create a schema of the DB
>mongoose.model			#To create a model out of the schema

